        <h2 class="gallery-title"><span class="media-prefix icon-gallery"></span>The most ridiculous claims made about Jeremy Corbyn</h2>
        <div class="images">
      <ul><li data-gallery-item="1" data-original="https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/styles/story_large/public/thumbnails/image/2015/09/29/14/jeremy-corbyn-3.jpg" style="background-image: url('/sites/all/themes/ines_themes/ines_theme/img/blank.gif');" class=""></li>
